name: Convert From B2C
query: select tabInvoices.invoice_date as 'Date',tabInvoices.name as 'Invoice Number',tabInvoices.room_number as 'Room No.',tabInvoices.guest_name as 'Guest Name',tabInvoices.confirmation_number as 'Confirmation No.',tabInvoices.gst_number as 'GST No.',tabInvoices.irn_generated as 'IRN Generated',tabInvoices.converted_from_b2c_by as 'Converted By',tabInvoices.converted_from_b2c_time as 'Converted Time' from tabInvoices where tabInvoices.converted_from_b2c= 'Yes' and (DATE(tabInvoices.creation) between %(from_date)s and %(to_date)s) order by tabInvoices.name
